{
  "chapter": "048",
  "title": "陈涉世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>人，字涉。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳夏</span>人，字叔。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>年轻时，曾经与人一起受雇耕田，有一次停下耕作走到田埂上，怅然叹息了很久，说：\"假如<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>了，大家不要互相忘记。\" 同伴们笑着回答说：\"你给人家耕田做工，哪里来的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>长叹一声说：\"唉，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">燕雀</span>怎能知道<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">鸿鹄之志</span>呢！\""
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年七月</span>，征发闾左贫民去戍守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渔阳</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九百人</span>屯驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大泽乡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>都在应征之列，担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">屯长</span>。恰逢天降大雨，道路不通，估计已经误了期限。按<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>规定，误期的都要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>首。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>于是商议说：\"如今<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">逃亡</span>也是死，起兵大事也是死，同样是死，为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">国</span>事而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>可以吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>苦于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的暴政已经很久了。我听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>是少子，不应当继位，应当继位的是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子扶苏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扶苏</span>因为屡次进谏的缘故，皇上派他在外领兵。如今有人听说他没有罪，却被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>害了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>大多听说他贤能，并不知道他已经死了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项燕</span>曾任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>将，屡次立功，爱护<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人都怀念他。有人认为他死了，有人认为他逃亡了。如今若真的以我们这些人诈称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子扶苏</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项燕</span>，为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>倡导，响应的人应该会很多。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>认为有道理。于是去占卜。卜者明白他们的用意，说：\"您们的事都能成功，会有功绩。但是您们占卜的事与鬼神有关吧！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>听了很高兴，想到鬼神之事，说：\"这是教我们先在众人中立威罢了。\"于是用朱砂在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>上写\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>王\"，放进别人用网捕到的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>腹中。士卒买了那<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>烹煮食用，发现<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>腹中的字条，本来就觉得奇怪。又暗中让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>到驻地旁边的丛林祠庙中，夜里生起篝<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">火</span>，模仿<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狐</span>狸叫声呼喊：\"大<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兴，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>王。\"士卒们夜里都惊恐。第二天，士卒中到处议论，都用手指、用目光注视<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>平素爱护部下，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>多愿意为他效力。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将尉</span>喝醉了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴广\">广（吴广）</span>故意多次说想要逃亡，激怒<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>，让他侮辱自己，以激怒众人。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>果然鞭笞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴广\">广（吴广）</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>拔出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴广\">广（吴广）</span>起身，夺过剑<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>协助他，一同<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了两个<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>。召集<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">徒属</span>说：\"诸位遇上大雨，都已误期，误期按律当<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>。即使不被斩，戍边而死的本来也要十分之六七。况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span>不死便罢，要死就要成就大名，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">王侯将相宁有种乎</span>！\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">徒属</span>都说：\"愿听从您的命令。\"于是诈称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子扶苏</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项燕</span>，顺从民众的意愿。袒露右臂，号称大<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。筑起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">坛</span>结盟，用<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>的头作祭。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大泽乡</span>，收集兵力后<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span>后，就命令<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">符离</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">葛婴</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲</span>以东之地。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铚</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">酂</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苦</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">柘</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">谯</span>，都<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span>了。一路行军收兵。等到到达<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六七百乘</span>，骑兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀</span>，士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守令</span>都不在，只有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守丞</span>在谯门中<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">迎战</span>。守丞没能取胜，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守丞</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">战死</span>，于是攻入<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">占据</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数天（时长）</span>之后，发号施令召集<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三老</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪杰</span>一同商议大事。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三老</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪杰</span>都说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>身披<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">坚</span>甲手执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">锐</span>兵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>无道之君，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>暴虐的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝，重立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>，论功应当称王。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>于是立为王，国号称<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">张楚</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "当这时，各郡县苦于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝官吏的，都<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">处刑</span>当地的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他们来响应<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>。于是任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴叔</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">假王</span>，统率<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>向西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。命令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武臣</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张耳</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈馀</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>地，命令<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汝阴</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邓宗</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江郡</span>。当这时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>聚集为一股者，多得数不清。"
    },
    "3.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">葛婴</span>到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东城</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">襄彊</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：葛婴\">婴（葛婴）</span>后来听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>已立，就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">襄彊</span>，回来报告。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">葛婴</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>命令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>北上<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李由</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">三川守</span>，守卫<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴叔</span>攻不下。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>征召国中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪杰</span>商议，任命<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上蔡</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">房君蔡赐</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上柱国</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周文</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>地的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤人</span>，曾经为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项燕</span>军中观测天象，侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>，自称熟悉兵事，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>授予他<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，向西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。一路行军收兵到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关</span>，有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千乘</span>，士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">戏</span>水，驻扎下来。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>命令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">少府</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>赦免<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郦山</span>的刑徒和奴隶所生之子，全部发动起来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>大军，将其全部<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周文</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>走，逃出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关</span>，停驻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曹阳</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二三月（时长）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>追击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span>他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周文</span>又逃到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渑池</span>驻扎<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多天（时长）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>发起<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>其军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周文</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刎颈</span>自杀，军队于是不战而溃。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武臣</span>到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈馀</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张耳</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召骚</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左右丞相</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>发怒，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逮捕</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">囚系</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武臣</span>等人的家属，想◉诛杀他们。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柱国</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>未<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">灭亡</span>就◉诛杀<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>的家属，这等于又制造一个<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。不如就势立他。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>于是派使者去祝贺<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，而把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武臣</span>等人的家属迁到宫中看守，并<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张耳\">耳（张耳）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张敖</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">成都君</span>，催促<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>兵赶快入关。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>共同商议说：\"王在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>地称王，并非<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的本意。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>如果<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，必然加兵于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。计策不如不要西进兵力，派使者向北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地来扩大自己。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>南靠<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大河</span>，北有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>即使战胜<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，也不敢制<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。如果<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>不能胜<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，必然倚重<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>乘<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>衰弊之机，可以在<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>实现抱负。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>认为有道理，于是不西进用兵，派遣原<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上谷</span>卒史<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩广</span>率兵北上<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>的旧<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪杰</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩广</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>已立王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>也已立王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>虽小，也是<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之国，希望<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩广</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩广\">广（韩广）</span>的母亲在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，不能这样做。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>人说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>正西面担忧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，南面担忧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，他们的力量不能禁止我们。况且以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的强盛，都不敢加害<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>的家属，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>又怎敢加害<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>的家属！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩广</span>认为有道理，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>的母亲及家属护送回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "7.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "在这时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>中<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取土地的人，多得数不清。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>北上<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>地到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">狄</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">狄</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">狄</span>令，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>，以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的军力反过来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周市\">市（周市）</span>的军队溃散，退回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地，想<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的后裔、原<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甯陵君咎</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏王</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：甯陵君咎\">咎（甯陵君咎）</span>在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>那里，不能回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地平定后，想一起<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>不肯。使者往返五次，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>才<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甯陵君咎</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏王</span>，送他<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">之国</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>最终担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田臧</span>等人一起商议说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周文\">周章（周文）</span>的军队已经<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">失败</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵旦夕将到，我们<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>城攻不下，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军一到，必定大败。不如留少量兵力，足以守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，用全部精兵迎击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军。如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">假王</span>骄傲，不懂得用兵的权变，不能和他商议，不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀他，事情恐怕要败。\"于是共同假借王命<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴叔</span>，把他的首级献给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>派使者赐予<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田臧</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">楚令尹</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，让他担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田臧</span>于是派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李归</span>等守卫<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>城，自己率领精兵西去在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>迎击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军。与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">交战</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田臧</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>，军队溃败。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>进兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李归</span>等于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>城下，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>他们，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李归</span>等<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">战死</span>。"
    },
    "8.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邓说</span>率兵驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">别将</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邓说</span>军队溃散逃回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铚</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍徐</span>率兵驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">许</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍徐</span>军队都溃散逃回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邓说</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "9.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>初立时，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陵</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦嘉</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铚</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董緤</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">符离</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃鸡石</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">取虑</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑布</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁疾</span>等都各自起事，率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东海守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庆</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郯</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>听说后，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武平君畔</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，统领<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郯</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">下军</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦嘉</span>不接受命令，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦嘉\">嘉（秦嘉）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span>，不愿意隶属于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：武平君畔\">武平君（武平君畔）</span>。他告诉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军吏</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：武平君畔\">武平君（武平君畔）</span>年少，不懂军事，不要听他的！\"于是假托王命<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武平君畔</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "10.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍徐</span>，进攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柱国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡赐\">房君（蔡赐）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">战死</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>又进兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>西的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张贺</span>军。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>出来督战，军队溃败，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张贺</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">战死</span>。"
    },
    "10.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">腊月</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汝阴</span>，又返回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下城父</span>，他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御</span>者<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他去投降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>，○谥号叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐王</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "11.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>原先的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">涓人</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕臣</span>组成苍头军，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新阳</span>起兵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>下<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span>，把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>又归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "12.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，命令<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铚</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋留</span>率兵平定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：宋留\">留（宋留）</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>了，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>又归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋留</span>不能攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>，就东行到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新蔡</span>，遇到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋留</span>率军投降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：宋留\">留（宋留）</span>押送到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">车裂</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：宋留\">留（宋留）</span>示众。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "13.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦嘉</span>等人听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>军队溃败出走，就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景驹</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，率兵到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方与</span>，想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span>城下。派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙庆</span>出使<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>，想联合兵力一起进军。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>说：\"听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>，不知道他的生死，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>怎么能不请示就立王！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙庆</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>不请示<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>就立王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>为什么要请示<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>才立王！况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>是首先起事的，当在<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>发号施令。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙庆</span>。"
    },
    "13.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左右校</span>再次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span>它。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕将军</span>逃走，收兵又聚集起来。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄱</span>地的盗<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">当阳君黥布</span>之兵合兵一处，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左右校</span>，在青波<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>他们，又把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。恰逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>之孙<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚义帝\">心（楚义帝）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "14.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>为王总共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六月（时长）</span>。已经为王，定都<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">故人</span>曾经和他一起受雇耕田的听说了，到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>来，敲宫门说：\"我要见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">涉（陈胜）</span>。\"宫门令想绑他。他自己辩解了好一会儿，才被放开，但门令不肯替他通报。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>出门，客人拦路呼叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">涉（陈胜）</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>听到了，就召见他，与他同乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>一同回宫。进入宫殿，看见殿堂屋宇<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帷帐</span>，客人说：\"真多啊！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">涉（陈胜）</span>做王真是气派深沉啊！\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人称\"多\"为\"夥\"，所以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>都传说\"夥<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">涉（陈胜）</span>为王\"，这话是从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>开始的。客人出入宫廷越来越放肆，讲述<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>的往事。有人劝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>说：\"客人愚昧无知，专门胡说八道，有损您的威严。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>了他。所有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">故人</span>都自动离去，从此没有人再亲近<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>了。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃房</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中正</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡武</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司过</span>，主管监察<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">徇</span>取土地归来，有不服从命令的，就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">囚系</span>起来治罪，把苛察当作忠诚。所不喜欢的人，不交给吏员，就自己处置。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈王</span>很信任他们。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>因此不亲附他，这就是他失败的原因。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "15.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>虽已死，但他所安置派遣的侯王<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>终于<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">灭亡</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，这是由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">涉（陈胜）</span>首先起事而来的。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>时为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>设置了守冢<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十家</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>，至今仍然享受<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">血食</span>之祭。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "16.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚先生</span>说：地形险阻，用来作为固守之凭借；兵甲<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">刑法</span>，用来治理国家。然而这些都还不足以凭恃。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>为根本，而把险阻<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>度作为枝叶，难道不是这样吗！我听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贾生</span>曾这样说道："
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "17.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦孝公</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">据</span>有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽函</span>的险固，拥有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍州</span>的地盘，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君臣</span>固守，以窥视<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室。他有席卷<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，囊括四海，并吞八荒的雄心。当这个时候，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商君</span>辅佐他，内立<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法度</span>，致力耕织，修治守战的装备；对外<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">连衡</span>而与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>争斗。于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>人拱手取得了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>以外的土地。"
    },
    "17.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝公\">孝公（秦孝公）</span>死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦惠文王\">惠文王（秦惠文王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦武王\">武王（秦武王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>承袭先业，沿用遗留的策略，向南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>，向西举取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>，向东攻取膏腴之地，收取要害之郡。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>恐惧，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">会盟</span>谋划削弱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>不惜<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">珍器重宝</span>和肥饶之地，以招致<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之士。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>缔结盟约，互相联为一体。在这个时候，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">孟尝（孟尝君）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：平原君\">平原（平原君）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：春申君\">春申（春申君）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：信陵君\">信陵（信陵君）</span>：这四位君子，都明智忠信，宽厚爱人，尊贤重士。以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">从</span>约连<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">衡</span>，联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>的兵众。于是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>之士有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甯越</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐尚</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杜赫</span>之类为他们谋划，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐明</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周勣</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈轸</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邵滑</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">翟景</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏厉</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>之辈沟通他们的意图，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">带他</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒良</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王廖</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵奢</span>之伦统领他们的军队。曾以十倍于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的土地、<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百万</span>的军队，面向<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关</span>而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>人打开<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关</span>门迎敌，九国之兵逃遁而不敢前进。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>没有损失一支<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矢</span>、一个<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">镞</span>的费用，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>就已经陷入困境。于是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">从</span>约解散、盟约<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">失败</span>，大家争相割地贿赂<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>有余力来制服他们的疲敝，追击逃败，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伏尸</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百万</span>，流<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">血</span>漂起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">橹</span>盾，凭借有利时机，宰割<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，分裂山河，强国请求臣服，弱国入朝。"
    },
    "17.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "\"这种局面沿续到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文王</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄襄王</span>，享国日短，国家无事。"
    },
    "17.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "\"等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>，发扬<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六世（时长）</span>的余威，挥动长鞭驾驭天下，吞并东西二<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">灭亡</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，登上至尊之位统制六合，手执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">敲朴</span>而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">鞭笞</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，威震四海。向南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">百越</span>之地，设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桂林</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">象郡</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">百越</span>之君低头<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">系</span>颈，听命于下吏。又派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>到北方修筑<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">长城</span>以守护边境，击退<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七百馀里</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>人不敢南下放牧<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>匹，士人也不敢张<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓</span>复仇。于是废弃<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>之道，焚烧<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">百家</span>之言，以愚弄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份·规范：黔首\">百姓（黔首）</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">毁坏</span>名城，◉杀戮<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪俊</span>，把<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>器收集到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，销毁<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">锋鍉</span>，铸成<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金人</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十二</span>，以削弱<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之民。然后踩着华山筑成城墙，凭借<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>作为护城河，据有亿丈高城，面临不测深溪以为固守。良将把守强<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弩</span>、要害之处，信臣精卒，陈列利<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>而盘查行人。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>已定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>的心意，自以为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>的险固，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金城</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">万世（时长）</span>之业。"
    },
    "17.5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>已死，余威还振慑着异域。然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>，瓮牖绳枢<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甕牖绳枢</span>之子，草野小民，迁徙之徒。才能不及中等之人，没有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲尼</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">墨翟</span>的贤明，没有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陶硃</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">猗顿</span>的富有。投身行伍之间，俯仰于阡陌之中，率领散乱疲惫的士卒，领着<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百</span>人之众，转而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">砍</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>作<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>器，举起<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竿</span>为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旗</span>帜，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>云集响应，背着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粮</span>食如影随形，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪俊</span>于是一起兴起而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">灭亡</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>。"
    },
    "17.6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "\"况且<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>并非小弱；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍州</span>之地，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽函</span>的险固依然如故。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>的地位，不比<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>之君尊贵；<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鉏櫌棘矜</span>，不比<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">句戟长铩</span>锋利；谪戍之众，不能与九国之师相比；深谋远虑、行军用兵之道，不如以前之士。然而成败变化相反，功业相反。如果让<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>之国与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>比量长短、比较权力，那就根本不能相提并论了。然而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>以狭小之地，获得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之权，控制八州而使其他六国朝见，历时<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百多年（时长）</span>。这以后把六合当家，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽函</span>为宫。一介之人发难而七庙<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">倾覆</span>，帝王身死人手，被<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>笑话，这是为什么？<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>不施，而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>守之势不同了。\""
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>纷乱，海内乏主， 群雄掎<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鹿</span>争胜，瞻<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">乌</span>观时势。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>首先发难，国号<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">张楚</span>。 凭借鬼怪之托，自比<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸿鹄</span>之志。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">葛婴</span>东征南下，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周文</span>西抗强敌。 先亲信<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃房</span>，又任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡武</span>。 夥颐之叹见<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，心腹之人不附。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span>是何等人，反噬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城父</span>！"
    }
  }
}